column1: #  pval_perm_SmallestpQTL: Permutation-adjusted p-value corresponding to the top eQTL variant (with the smallest nominal p-value) for each protein.
# pval_nominal_threshold: The nomila pvalue threshold used to determine significant SNP_gene associations within each gene.
